DANCING: Dancing with trained skill

Category: Creative
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Genuine skill at dance, from social dancing to formal performance.
Useful anywhere a character needs to look graceful, blend into a
social event, or simply put on a good show.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, singing, art
